came put,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "driven, back: became put,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "placed, behind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "after: became behind, posterior,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "last: he remained behind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the rear; held back, hung back, lagged behind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "delayed; was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, backward,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "late: it was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, kept back, postponed, put off, procrastinated, deferred, delayed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "retarded: contr. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taqad~ama", "text_ar": "تَقَدَّمَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AstA^xar", "text_ar": "استاخَر", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is syn. therewith; (S, K:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^x~r", "text_ar": "اخّر", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^oxiyrN", "text_ar": "تَاْخِيرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", signifies the same, being intrans. as well as trans. (K.) An ex. of the latter occurs in a saying of Mohammad to 'Omar:"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ean~Yi", "text_ar": "عَنّىِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ax~iro", "text_ar": "اَخِّرْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Retire thou from me:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or the meaning is,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ax~iroEan~iY raA^oyaka", "text_ar": "اَخِّرْعَنِّى رَاْيَكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "hold thou back from me thine opinion;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "reserve thou thine opinion until after mine shall have been given"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^ax~ira Eanohu taA^ax~urapF waAHidapF", "text_ar": "تَاَخِّرَ عَنْهُ تَاَخُّرَةً وَاحِدَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He went back,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, once"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Lh.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tA^x~r Eani Al$~aYo'i", "text_ar": "تاخّر عَنِ الشَّىْءِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA^amori", "text_ar": "الاَمْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He went back,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from the thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the affair: he was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, behind, behindhand,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "backward, with respect to it: he held back, hung back, refrained,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "abstained, from it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eanohu", "text_ar": "عَنْهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AstA^xr", "text_ar": "استاخر", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the same. (The Lexicons in many places.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faA_i*aA jaA='a", "text_ar": "فَاـِذَا جَا=ءَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEapF", "text_ar": "سَاعَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajaluhumo laA yasotaA^oxiruwna", "text_ar": "اَجَلُهُمْ لَا يَسْتَاْخِرُونَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the Kur vii. 32 and other places, means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And when their time is come,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "for punishment,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "they will not remain behind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or be respited, ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "any while,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the shortest time:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "they shall not seek to remain behind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by reason of intense terror. (Bd.)"}], "source_refs": ["TA", "S", "K"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}